# International Debt Analysis — SQL Queries

This document contains the **30 SQL analytical queries** used in the *International Debt Analysis System* project. Queries are grouped into **Basic**, **Intermediate**, and **Advanced** levels and are written against a table named `international_debt` with the following assumed schema:

| Column          | Description                          |
|-----------------|---------------------------------------|
| `country_name`  | Name of the country                  |
| `country_code`  | ISO country code                     |
| `indicator_name`| Name of the debt indicator           |
| `indicator_code`| Code of the debt indicator           |
| `debt`          | Debt value (in USD)                  |

> 💡 Adjust table/column names as per your actual database schema.

